@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram

state StartChoice <<choice>>
state AccountCreationChoice <<choice>>
state LoginChoice <<choice>>
state ApplicationChoice <<choice>>
state StatusViewChoice <<choice>>
state StatusCheckChoice <<choice>>
state ApplicationCancelChoice <<choice>>
state DetailModificationChoice <<choice>>
state DetailViewChoice <<choice>>
state FeedbackChoice <<choice>>
state EndJoin <<choice>>

[*] --> AccountCreationChoice

AccountCreationChoice --> Register
AccountCreationChoice --> LoginChoice

Register : do / Fill details
Register : exit / Registration successful

LoginChoice --> Login
LoginChoice --> InvalidUser

Login : entry / Registered user
Login : do / Enter login credentials
Login : exit / Valid username and password

InvalidUser : entry / Invalid login or invalid registration
InvalidUser : do / Block entry to system
InvalidUser : exit / Abnormal termination

ApplicationChoice --> ApplyForVisa
ApplicationChoice --> CancelApplication
ApplicationChoice --> ModifyDetails
ApplicationChoice --> ViewDetails
ApplicationChoice --> ViewPurpose
ApplicationChoice --> StatusViewChoice
ApplicationChoice --> StatusCheckChoice
ApplicationChoice --> FeedbackChoice

ApplyForVisa : entry / User logged in
ApplyForVisa : do / Apply for visa, make payment
ApplyForVisa : exit / Application accepted

CancelApplication : entry / User logged in
CancelApplication : do / Cancel application
CancelApplication : exit / Application cancelled

ModifyDetails : entry / User logged in
ModifyDetails : do / Modify user details
ModifyDetails : exit / Details modified

ViewDetails : entry / User logged in
ViewDetails : do / View user details
ViewDetails : exit / Details viewed

ViewPurpose : entry / User logged in
ViewPurpose : do / View visa application purpose
ViewPurpose : exit / Purpose viewed

StatusViewChoice --> ViewStatus
StatusViewChoice --> StatusCheckChoice

ViewStatus : entry / User logged in
ViewStatus : do / View visa status
ViewStatus : exit / Status viewed

StatusCheckChoice --> CheckStatus
StatusCheckChoice --> ViewStatus

CheckStatus : entry / User logged in
CheckStatus : do / Check visa status
CheckStatus : exit / Status checked

FeedbackChoice --> GiveFeedback
FeedbackChoice --> StatusCheckChoice

GiveFeedback : entry / User logged in
GiveFeedback : do / Provide feedback
GiveFeedback : exit / Feedback given

DetailModificationChoice --> ModifyDetails
DetailModificationChoice --> DetailViewChoice

DetailModificationChoice --> ModifyDetails
DetailViewChoice --> ViewDetails

ModifyDetails --> DetailViewChoice
ViewDetails --> DetailModificationChoice

StatusCheckChoice --> ViewStatus
ViewStatus --> StatusCheckChoice

FeedbackChoice --> EndJoin
StatusCheckChoice --> EndJoin

EndJoin --> [*]

@enduml
